sketch.compiler.ast.core.exprs.regens

Class ExprChoiceUnary

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENode
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.exprs.Expression
        • sketch.compiler.ast.core.exprs.regens.ExprChoiceUnary

  • public class ExprChoiceUnary
extends Expression
    Unary operation on an operand which has unknown choice. This is used for generating choices in a regular-expression style. This kind of choices is just a syntactic sugar and are always boiled down to using holes (ExprStar).
